en-US.title: headspace Gosford- Mental Health Support Center
en-US.description: headspace Gosford is a dedicated support center for young individuals and their families to obtain mental health resources and services. They offer culturally suitable services that acknowledge and celebrate diversity eliminating all forms of discrimination in provision of health services. Their facility is equipped to accommodate people from different ethnicity, lifestyle choice, faith, and particularly sexual orientation and gender identity. Available services include professional consultations like 1-on-1 chat, community contributions, and personal mental health toolkit development.
